## 6) Monitoring dan Operasional Harian

Wajib dipantau:
- Health API (`/health`, DB check internal-only).
- Error rate 5xx.
- Failed login spike.
- Disk growth (uploads, logs, backup).
- Umur sertifikat/tunnel Cloudflare.

Jadwal:
- Harian: cek service + error log + failed login.
- Mingguan: test restore backup sampel.
- Bulanan: rotasi secret kunci kritikal.

